dreamwave-player is a retro-inspired aesthetic music player designed in Framer with interactive audio controls and animated vinyl visuals.
The project features two customizable themes — a soft pink dreamy interface and a blue retro-inspired variant — along with smooth transitions, popup overlays, and a dropdown menu system for navigating themes and player options.

Pink Theme → https://plain-feature-737962.framer.app/
Blue Theme → https://grey-location-026191.framer.app/

Built with a mix of Framer design and custom frontend logic to create an interactive nostalgic music-player experience.
